_:Nf8fa49e40e62453f9e4a811b91c13d05 <http://schema.org/description> "Sport England (SE) helps people and communities across the country get a sporting habit for life. It also protects existing sports provision and must be consulted on any planning applications that affect playing fields in England. SE is an executive non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Department for Culture, Media and Sport ." .
